@NODE "Mail_8" " Any takers? "
From: Curt Esser <camge@amigaonline.net>
Date: 10-10-00 02:53:32
Subject: @{b}Any takers?@{ub}

Hi everyone,

Since I am now working on a PC version of my Crazy8's card game, I have
decided to pass on the Amiga version to anyone who is interested in
developing it further.

I have had many requests for a GFX card compatabile version, but I never had
a GFX card form my Amiga (and I still don't) so if anybody wants to do this,
or anything else with the game, contact me at my personal email address.

The source code isn't the prettiest, but it does have lots of comments so
you should be able to work out what is going on.

BTW, the source code itself (though not the most recent version) can be
found on the Blitz section of my website if you want to take a peek before
volunteering.

                             Yours electronically,
                             Curt Esser
                             <camge@amigaonline.net>
                             http://members.nbci.com/curt_esser/


@ENDNODE

