@NODE "Mail_76" " JSR's "
From: Tony Rolfe <edgewater@shoalhaven.net.au>
Date: 10-14-00 03:19:58
Subject: @{b}JSR's@{ub}

I know that you can't gosub from inside a function to ad address
outside the function.   (The following doesn't work...)

Function.b Thing{}

Gosub label

end function

label
return

Can you do the equivalent using JSR/RTS, e.g.

Function.b Thing{variable.l}

GetReg a0,variable
JSR  0(a0)

end function

Ret.b = Thing{?label}


label
RTS

Will this 
a) work
b) completely stuff up the stack
c) work with limitations
d) dunno

Thanks for the assistance


-- 
Tony Rolfe
Amiga 2000, 68030/25, 1+8Mb
www.shoalhaven.net.au/edgewater
ICQ #51271965
