@NODE "Mail_98" " Re: Menus and fun "
From: Nick Clover <bauk@uksysops.com>
Date: 10-20-00 10:19:58
Subject: @{b}Re: Menus and fun@{ub}

Hello KristianGK@aol.com

On 19-Oct-00, you wrote:

> Hi,

> I just got round to downloading the RIGTLibs and it works nicely :)
> BTW is it possible to tell whether any (external) sound is being played in a 
> blitz program?

Yep, Check out my SNDMon program on aminet. Here's the main line of interest.

stat.s=Right$(Bin$(Peek.w($dff002)),4)

this returns a four character string eg. "0000" telling you the status of the audio channels. 

> Thanks to all who helped,
> Kris,


