Hmmm... I'm not sure myself. I don't have the docs to hand at the minute,
I'll go and check the autodocs now. It's relatively easy to set up a TAB
cycle list though.

There is an #MUIA_String_AdvanceOnCR tag which makes the return key behave
like the TAB key, moving between gadgets in the cycle chain. I'm not sure if
this is what you want, but it sounds pretty close at least :-)

