@NODE "Mail_116" " Re: MUICycleSet "
From: David McMinn <D.Mcminn@eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Date: 10-06-00 15:59:11
Subject: @{b}Re: MUICycleSet@{ub}

Hi Deftone

> MUISetCycle #MUI_Cycle1,Nat$ <-this not work how should i set it up right?

This is because you need to use a numeric variable when calling MUISetCycle. 
Nat$ is a string variable. You could do something like this:

Nat.w = Val(FindToolValue("Nation"))
NPrint Nat
MUISetCycle #MUI_Cycle1,Nat


