Hi John,

----- Original Message -----
From: John Mason <ah210@chebucto.ns.ca>

>   Does anyone know how to trap RMB clicks and prevent the menu bar from
> showing up?  I want to be able to do something when the right button is
> pressed, but I don't want the menus to flash at the same time.  I know it
> can be done because DPaint and PPaint for example do the same thing.

The easiest way is to use the command "MenusOff" right after opening your
window.

This makes that window "immune" to menu-events (right mouse button clicks)
so now you can read the right mouse button and do whatever you want.

