As I recall, the installation on the Blitz CD doesn't install ANY of the
libraries at all, nor the BSS either.

So, if the source in question is using anything that is not in the Acidlibs
file, you won't have any luck...

I had to install 'em all by hand  (the regular Blitz libraries, I mean)

But, David, didn't you make an updated intall script that takes care of this
problem?

