@NODE "Mail_169" " Re: Timer "
From: Toby Zu dveld <tzuyd@crosswinds.net>
Date: 10-09-00 00:12:29
Subject: @{b}Re: Timer@{ub}

Hello Lukas

On 06-Oct-00, you wrote:

LS> I use commands ResetTimer and Timer.
LS> Timer returns number of 50ths since machine starup.
LS> Is it dependent on PAL/NTSC ?

Yup.  You can use NTSC (value.b=#NTSC#) to see which mode the machine
is running in.

